# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:20
translate spanish reba8_d1862604:

    # "My phone starts buzzing. Reba's calling."
    "Mi teléfono empieza a vibrar. Es Reba."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:23
translate spanish reba8_bea5e8cb:

    # pc "Hello?"
    pc "¿Hola?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:24
translate spanish reba8_6f14a2e1:

    # rb "Good morning, sunshine! Oh, did I wake you up? I'm sorry!"
    rb "¡Buenos días, rayito de sol! Oh, ¿te he despertado? ¡Lo siento!"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:25
translate spanish reba8_f259614b:

    # rb "I was just wondering if you wanted to hang out this afternoon."
    rb "Me preguntaba si te apetecía quedar esta tarde."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:27
translate spanish reba8_985f82ca:

    # rb "Was thinking about taking the truck out mudding. You wanna come?"
    rb "Estaba pensando en sacar la camioneta a hacer «mudding». ¿Quieres venir?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:30
translate spanish reba8mudding_6cec19f1:

    # pc "What's mudding?"
    pc "¿Qué es el «mudding»?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:32
translate spanish reba8mudding_e7087767:

    # rb "You never heard of mudding?"
    rb "¿Nunca has oído hablar del «mudding»?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:34
translate spanish reba8mudding_b6ed8158:

    # rb "You really are a city boy!"
    rb "¡De verdad que eres un chico de ciudad!"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:35
translate spanish reba8mudding_e360ee19:

    # rb "Mudding is when you take your truck, or 4-wheeler, or whatever out into a muddy place and drive through mud."
    rb "El «mudding» es cuando coges tu camioneta, o tu quad, o lo que sea, y te vas a un sitio embarrado para conducir por el barro."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:36
translate spanish reba8mudding_a8bf8c06:

    # rb "You sling that stuff all over the place, make a big mess."
    rb "Salpicas por todas partes, lo dejas todo hecho un desastre."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:37
translate spanish reba8mudding_9408222a:

    # rb "It's fun!"
    rb "¡Es divertido!"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:39
translate spanish reba8mudding_d01eb8f7:

    # rb "So you want to come mudding with me?"
    rb "¿Así que quieres venir a hacer «mudding» conmigo?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:46
translate spanish reba8mudding_90947dda:

    # rb "Oh okay. Well maybe next week then."
    rb "Ah, vale. Bueno, quizá la semana que viene entonces."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:50
translate spanish reba8mudding_e88ebc4a:

    # rb "Okay, I'll call you then. Hope you have a great day, [pcname]."
    rb "Vale, te llamaré entonces. Espero que tengas un buen día, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:51
translate spanish reba8mudding_19e6f6ea:

    # pc "You too Reba. Bye."
    pc "Tú también, Reba. Adiós."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:56
translate spanish reba8mudding_d3af0ef5:

    # rb "You're just not interested at all?"
    rb "¿Es que no te interesa en absoluto?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:57
translate spanish reba8mudding_fdf33919:

    # pc "No, I'm not. Sorry."
    pc "No, no me interesa. Lo siento."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:59
translate spanish reba8mudding_24e974ff:

    # rb "Okay then. Take care, [pcname]."
    rb "Vale, entonces. Cuídate, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:60
translate spanish reba8mudding_dbe309fc:

    # rb "Bye."
    rb "Adiós."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:63
translate spanish reba8mudding_273bc4d3:

    # "She hangs up. I guess that's it for me and Reba. Oh well - plenty of others out there I'm more interested in."
    "Cuelga. Supongo que se acabó lo mío con Reba. Bueno, hay muchas otras por ahí que me interesan más."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:68
translate spanish reba8mudding_5cc21e87:

    # rb "Yay! Come on out here then! I'll start getting ready."
    rb "¡Sí! ¡Pues ven aquí! Voy a empezar a prepararme."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:69
translate spanish reba8mudding_2c0a751f:

    # pc "Okay, see you in a bit."
    pc "Vale, nos vemos en un rato."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:70
translate spanish reba8mudding_9cdb897f:

    # rb "I can't wait! This is gonna be so dang fun!"
    rb "¡No puedo esperar! ¡Esto va a ser tan divertido!"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:73
translate spanish reba8mudding_f8872536:

    # "She hangs up and I go get dressed and head out towards her trailer."
    "Cuelga y yo me voy a vestir y salgo hacia su caravana."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:78
translate spanish reba8mudding_1e97ea52:

    # "When I get to her trailer, she's already outside waiting for me."
    "Cuando llego a su caravana, ella ya está fuera esperándome."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:79
translate spanish reba8mudding_611dcce8:

    # rb "Hey, [pcname]."
    rb "Hola, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:80
translate spanish reba8mudding_ee516682:

    # pc "Hey, Reba. You're looking cute."
    pc "Hola, Reba. Estás monísima."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:82
translate spanish reba8mudding_20522f33:

    # rb "Thanks! Just some old overalls that I don't care about getting muddy."
    rb "¡Gracias! Solo son unos viejos pantalones de trabajo que no me importa que se ensucien de barro."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:83
translate spanish reba8mudding_1a0f92f5:

    # pc "Well you look great."
    pc "Pues tú estás estupenda."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:84
translate spanish reba8mudding_6bf9d827:

    # pc "Your brother isn't going to be coming with us, is he?"
    pc "Tu hermano no va a venir con nosotros, ¿verdad?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:86
translate spanish reba8mudding_cd9c66f2:

    # rb "Nah, he's out with his friends right now and won't be back for a while."
    rb "No, ahora mismo está fuera con sus amigos y no volverá hasta dentro de un rato."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:87
translate spanish reba8mudding_3bbcece5:

    # rb "So, let's go. I'm looking forward to this."
    rb "Bueno, vamos. Tengo muchas ganas de que llegue esto."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:90
translate spanish reba8mudding_bac3c1f7:

    # "I follow her over to a truck that is not the one I expected to see."
    "La sigo hasta una camioneta que no es la que esperaba ver."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:91
translate spanish reba8mudding_701cd65b:

    # pc "This is your truck? What happened to the old red classic one?"
    pc "¿Esta es tu camioneta? ¿Qué ha pasado con la clásica roja de siempre?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:92
translate spanish reba8mudding_ed741e5e:

    # rb "Oh I left it at the garage today. Not going to take that one out mudding, of course. That's just for weekend drives."
    rb "Ah, hoy la he dejado en el taller. No voy a llevarla a hacer barro, claro. Esa es solo para dar vueltas los fines de semana."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:93
translate spanish reba8mudding_b0f293e1:

    # rb "This one I'm not afraid to beat up a little."
    rb "A esta no me da miedo darle un poco de caña."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:96
translate spanish reba8mudding_9138b610:

    # rb "You ready to do this?"
    rb "¿Estás listo para esto?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:97
translate spanish reba8mudding_69f1deb2:

    # pc "Sure, let's go."
    pc "Claro, vamos."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:98
translate spanish reba8mudding_8e844e87:

    # rb "I know this one spot where there's ALWAYS mud. I'll take you there."
    rb "Conozco un sitio donde SIEMPRE hay barro. Te llevaré allí."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:101
translate spanish reba8mudding_c74fb292:

    # "She drives us out into the middle of nowhere, taking curving backroads until I'm completely lost."
    "Nos lleva a medio de la nada, por carreteras secundarias sinuosas hasta que me pierdo por completo."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:102
translate spanish reba8mudding_d33cf134:

    # "She seems to know exactly where she's going, but there's no way I would be able to find my way back through this maze of paths that could barely be called roads."
    "Parece saber exactamente adónde va, pero yo no sería capaz de encontrar el camino de vuelta por este laberinto de senderos que apenas se pueden llamar carreteras."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:103
translate spanish reba8mudding_16815133:

    # "Then she parks in front of a muddy path through the forest in front of us. "
    "Luego aparca frente a un camino embarrado que atraviesa el bosque que tenemos delante. "

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:106
translate spanish reba8mudding_0f04ea1b:

    # "She looks over at me, a somewhat unsettling smile on her face."
    "Me mira, con una sonrisa un poco inquietante en la cara."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:107
translate spanish reba8mudding_8e751324:

    # rb "Are you ready?"
    rb "¿Estás listo?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:108
translate spanish reba8mudding_5a8379d3:

    # pc "Uh... sure."
    pc "Eh... claro."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:109
translate spanish reba8mudding_0d43968d:

    # rb "Okay, get your phone out and keep time for me. I've done this track in one minute and five seconds, hitting all the mud pits before. I wanna to see if I can beat that time."
    rb "Vale, saca tu móvil y cronometra el tiempo para mí. He hecho este recorrido en un minuto y cinco segundos, pasando por todos los charcos de barro. Quiero ver si puedo batir ese tiempo."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:110
translate spanish reba8mudding_63023601:

    # pc "Okay."
    pc "Vale."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:111
translate spanish reba8mudding_5d0cf67b:

    # "I fumble my phone out, get my finger over the start button of the stopwatch app, and then start to count down."
    "Saco mi móvil a tientas, pongo el dedo sobre el botón de inicio de la aplicación del cronómetro y empiezo la cuenta atrás."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:112
translate spanish reba8mudding_f184bd09:

    # rb "Go!"
    rb "¡Ya!"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:115
translate spanish reba8mudding_98515560:

    # "She pushes the pedal all the way down, causing the tires to spin for just a moment before they gain traction and launch us forward."
    "Pisa el acelerador a fondo, haciendo que las ruedas patinen un instante antes de que ganen tracción y nos lancen hacia delante."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:116
translate spanish reba8mudding_ac5744a1:

    # "I'm barely able to hold onto my phone as I'm slammed backwards in the seat."
    "Apenas puedo sujetar el móvil mientras me empuja hacia atrás contra el asiento."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:117
translate spanish reba8mudding_8dc485bd:

    # "Maybe I should have worn a seat belt? I'm not even sure this truck has seat belts!"
    "¿Quizás debería haberme puesto el cinturón de seguridad? ¡Ni siquiera estoy seguro de que esta camioneta tenga cinturones de seguridad!"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:120
translate spanish reba8mudding_5562507a:

    # "The truck barrels ahead and hits a large mud pit, sending mud flying into the air and bouncing me about in the cabin."
    "La camioneta avanza a toda velocidad y se mete en un gran charco de barro, haciendo que el barro salte por los aires y me sacuda por toda la cabina."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:121
translate spanish reba8mudding_a90c1d29:

    # rb "Wooohoooo!"
    rb "¡Wooohoooo!"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:122
translate spanish reba8mudding_89afb209:

    # "She cheers and doesn't slow down at all as she spins through the next turn and on to the next mud pit."
    "Ella grita de alegría y no reduce la velocidad en absoluto mientras toma la siguiente curva y se adentra en el siguiente charco de barro."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:125
translate spanish reba8mudding_c2cf0ebc:

    # "The truck slides, and me along with it, every time we turn a corner."
    "La camioneta se desliza, y yo con ella, cada vez que tomamos una curva."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:128
translate spanish reba8mudding_8ce22517:

    # "Every time she hits a mud pit, we spray more mud all over the truck."
    "Cada vez que se mete en un charco de barro, salpicamos más barro por toda la camioneta."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:129
translate spanish reba8mudding_95dfd36d:

    # "I hold my hand against the ceiling to try to keep myself in my seat."
    "Apoyo la mano contra el techo para intentar mantenerme en mi asiento."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:130
translate spanish reba8mudding_b6be7db2:

    # rb "Hold on to your butt! This last one is a real hoosawhatsit."
    rb "¡Agárrate bien! Este último es un auténtico desmadre."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:133
translate spanish reba8mudding_9e1718b9:

    # "We keep going faster, the windshield is covered with mud to the point that I'm not sure how she can even see anymore."
    "Seguimos acelerando, el parabrisas está tan cubierto de barro que no sé cómo puede ver nada."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:134
translate spanish reba8mudding_37c878ad:

    # rb "We're coming up on the finish, get your stopwatch ready!"
    rb "¡Nos acercamos a la meta, prepara el cronómetro!"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:135
translate spanish reba8mudding_f514d106:

    # pc "Oh thank God."
    pc "Oh, gracias a Dios."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:136
translate spanish reba8mudding_799b862b:

    # rb "Okay... now!"
    rb "Vale... ¡ya!"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:139
translate spanish reba8mudding_b7684910:

    # "Finally Reba presses on the brakes and the truck lurches to a stop. I let out a breath I didn't realize I'd been holding."
    "Por fin, Reba pisa el freno y la camioneta se detiene con una sacudida. Exhalo un suspiro que ni me había dado cuenta de que estaba conteniendo."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:140
translate spanish reba8mudding_1dbb6329:

    # rb "So? How did I do?"
    rb "¿Y bien? ¿Qué tal lo he hecho?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:141
translate spanish reba8mudding_f6466edf:

    # "I look at the time on the stopwatch."
    "Miro el tiempo en el cronómetro."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:142
translate spanish reba8mudding_7270a13f:

    # pc "One minute, three seconds."
    pc "Un minuto y tres segundos."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:143
translate spanish reba8mudding_b149628e:

    # rb "New record! Yes!"
    rb "¡Nuevo récord! ¡Sí!"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:144
translate spanish reba8mudding_8658f887:

    # rb "That was fun, right?"
    rb "Ha sido divertido, ¿verdad?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:145
translate spanish reba8mudding_89a6c21b:

    # pc "Yeah. Fun."
    pc "Sí. Divertido."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:146
translate spanish reba8mudding_7d646560:

    # rb "Good, because I think we can do better. Let's do it again!"
    rb "Bien, porque creo que podemos hacerlo mejor. ¡Vamos a repetirlo!"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:149
translate spanish reba8mudding_bd620e81:

    # "We spend the next hour or so driving around the mud track until the truck is completely covered, and I have completely lost feeling in my ass."
    "Pasamos la siguiente hora más o menos dando vueltas por la pista de barro hasta que la camioneta queda completamente cubierta y yo he perdido por completo la sensibilidad en el trasero."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:150
translate spanish reba8mudding_343cd1cb:

    # "Reba has a blast, and though I'm terrified that we'll get stuck or crash into a tree or something, after a bit, I start to have a fun just watching her have fun."
    "Reba se lo pasa en grande y, aunque me aterra que nos quedemos atascados o choquemos contra un árbol o algo así, al cabo de un rato empiezo a divertirme solo viéndola divertirse."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:153
translate spanish reba8mudding_973634d2:

    # "Then she finally has her fill and we head back to her trailer."
    "Luego, por fin, se cansa y volvemos a su caravana."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:156
translate spanish reba8mudding_05492d38:

    # "She pulls in and parks in the field near her trailer and turns towards me."
    "Se detiene y aparca en el campo cerca de su caravana y se gira hacia mí."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:159
translate spanish reba8mudding_75a03e1e:

    # rb "So did you have fun?"
    rb "¿Te has divertido?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:160
translate spanish reba8mudding_a96bbb2c:

    # pc "I did. I wasn't sure if I would, and I was a little worried at first, but yeah, it was really fun."
    pc "Sí. No estaba segura de si lo haría, y al principio estaba un poco preocupada, pero sí, ha sido muy divertido."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:161
translate spanish reba8mudding_aeccbbbf:

    # pc "I don't envy you having to wash this truck though. Getting all that dirt off is not going to be easy."
    pc "Aunque no te envidio por tener que lavar esta camioneta. Quitar toda esa suciedad no va a ser fácil."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:162
translate spanish reba8mudding_513ca920:

    # rb "I don't mind though. It's okay to get a little dirty every once in a while."
    rb "Pero no me importa. No pasa nada por ensuciarse un poco de vez en cuando."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:165
translate spanish reba8mudding_2c34965d:

    # "Without warning, she slides over and straddles me, sitting on my lap and kissing me hungrily."
    "Sin previo aviso, se desliza hacia mí y se sienta a horcajadas sobre mi regazo, besándome con avidez."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:166
translate spanish reba8mudding_1afe0aad:

    # "Her hands are all over me, caressing, pulling me closer as she grinds her hips on my lap."
    "Sus manos me recorren todo el cuerpo, acariciándome, acercándome a ella mientras frota sus caderas contra mi regazo."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:167
translate spanish reba8mudding_b05dede8:

    # rb "You feel so good."
    rb "Me haces sentir tan bien."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:168
translate spanish reba8mudding_1ddd540f:

    # pc "Should we be doing this here?"
    pc "¿Deberíamos estar haciendo esto aquí?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:169
translate spanish reba8mudding_f3c90719:

    # rb "I just want to kiss you a little. I'm not planning on having sex with you."
    rb "Solo quiero besarte un poco. No tengo intención de acostarme contigo."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:170
translate spanish reba8mudding_78efb177:

    # rb "At least not right here, right now."
    rb "Al menos no aquí y ahora."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:171
translate spanish reba8mudding_db7d54af:

    # rb "But geez, I want to. Really bad."
    rb "Pero, joder, quiero hacerlo. Muchísimo."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:174
translate spanish reba8mudding_01b84f46:

    # "Suddenly, the moment is broken by a loud banging on the window."
    "De repente, el momento se ve interrumpido por unos fuertes golpes en la ventanilla."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:175
translate spanish reba8mudding_b1399e56:

    # mk "You get the fuck off my sister!"
    mk "¡Quítate de encima de mi hermana, joder!"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:176
translate spanish reba8mudding_f430f39f:

    # mk "Get out of there right now!"
    mk "¡Sal de ahí ahora mismo!"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:177
translate spanish reba8mudding_d3c077e8:

    # rb "Oh no."
    rb "Oh, no."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:178
translate spanish reba8mudding_da60c5f6:

    # mk "Come on out now!"
    mk "¡Sal ahora mismo!"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:181
translate spanish reba8mudding_ac03042f:

    # "We both get out of the car and Reba slams the door behind her."
    "Los dos salimos del coche y Reba da un portazo detrás de ella."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:182
translate spanish reba8mudding_f3332dc9:

    # rb "Mickey, we talked about this!"
    rb "Mickey, ¡ya hablamos de esto!"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:183
translate spanish reba8mudding_65738771:

    # mk "If you think I'm gonna let this asshole fuck my sister right outside of my house, you're outta your goddamn mind."
    mk "Si crees que voy a dejar que este gilipollas se folle a mi hermana justo delante de mi casa, estás completamente loco."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:184
translate spanish reba8mudding_94d699fc:

    # rb "We wasn't, Mickey! We wasn't doing anything!"
    rb "¡No estábamos, Mickey! ¡No estábamos haciendo nada!"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:185
translate spanish reba8mudding_25793dab:

    # mk "And you ain't gonna, cause I'm gonna teach this boy a lesson!"
    mk "¡Y no lo vas a hacer, porque voy a darle una lección a este chico!"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:188
translate spanish reba8mudding_ccda4aeb:

    # "It's obvious that Reba isn't going to be able to talk any sense into him this time."
    "Es obvio que Reba no va a poder hacerle entrar en razón esta vez."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:189
translate spanish reba8mudding_c5f2f949:

    # "He comes at me, fist raised."
    "Se abalanza sobre mí, con el puño en alto."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:192
translate spanish reba8mudding_0552f3ff:

    # "All that training with Tammy comes in handy. This guy is nothing compared to the punches that she has thrown at me."
    "Todo ese entrenamiento con Tammy me viene muy bien. Este tipo no es nada comparado con los puñetazos que ella me ha dado."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:203
translate spanish reba8mudding_781f13e4:

    # "I step into the punch, knocking his hand to the side and countering with a right hook to the side of his jaw. It lands with a satisfying crack."
    "Me adelanto al puñetazo, desviando su mano hacia un lado y contraatacando con un gancho de derecha en el lado de la mandíbula. Impacta con un crujido satisfactorio."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:206
translate spanish reba8mudding_510db655:

    # "I go in for another punch, but Reba jumps between us."
    "Voy a por otro puñetazo, pero Reba se interpone entre nosotros."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:207
translate spanish reba8mudding_53c501af:

    # rb "No! Stop fighting!"
    rb "¡No! ¡Dejad de pelear!"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:208
translate spanish reba8mudding_ceeca70d:

    # mk "I'm gonna fucking kill him, get out of my way!"
    mk "¡Voy a matarlo, joder, quítate de en medio!"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:209
translate spanish reba8mudding_b769b5ca:

    # rb "No you're not!"
    rb "¡No, no lo vas a hacer!"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:210
translate spanish reba8mudding_d9fe3e76:

    # pc "She's right, if you come at me again I'm going to lay you out."
    pc "Tiene razón, si vuelves a venir a por mí te voy a dejar fuera de combate."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:211
translate spanish reba8mudding_0caaea36:

    # mk "That was a lucky punch you son of a bitch!"
    mk "¡Ese ha sido un golpe de suerte, hijo de puta!"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:212
translate spanish reba8mudding_a2a7eb65:

    # rb "STOP!"
    rb "¡BASTA!"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:213
translate spanish reba8mudding_54567e75:

    # rb "Just go, [pcname]. I'll talk to you later."
    rb "Vete ya, [pcname]. Hablaremos más tarde."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:214
translate spanish reba8mudding_61f77a4c:

    # pc "Sure."
    pc "Claro."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:218
translate spanish reba8mudding_bdfd4cce:

    # "That training with Tammy comes in handy. This guy is nothing compared to the punches that she had thrown at me."
    "Todo ese entrenamiento con Tammy me viene muy bien. Este tipo no es nada comparado con los puñetazos que ella me ha dado."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:219
translate spanish reba8mudding_6c41ac4b:

    # "I easily step outside of his punch and prepare to dodge whatever he has to follow it up with."
    "Esquivo fácilmente su puñetazo y me preparo para esquivar lo que sea que tenga para seguir."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:222
translate spanish reba8mudding_d02d2a53:

    # "Before he can throw another one though, Reba jumps between us."
    "Sin embargo, antes de que pueda lanzar otro, Reba se interpone entre nosotros."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:223
translate spanish reba8mudding_53c501af_1:

    # rb "No! Stop fighting!"
    rb "¡No! ¡Dejad de pelear!"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:224
translate spanish reba8mudding_ace0e755:

    # mk "This asshole needs to be taught a lesson!"
    mk "¡Hay que darle una lección a este gilipollas!"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:225
translate spanish reba8mudding_64d142d4:

    # pc "I didn't do anything."
    pc "Yo no he hecho nada."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:226
translate spanish reba8mudding_c9511b36:

    # mk "You're trying to fuck my sister!"
    mk "¡Estás intentando tirarte a mi hermana!"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:227
translate spanish reba8mudding_a40a4d44:

    # rb "We didn't do nothing, Mickey! Stop!"
    rb "¡No hemos hecho nada, Mickey! ¡Para!"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:228
translate spanish reba8mudding_54567e75_1:

    # rb "Just go, [pcname]. I'll talk to you later."
    rb "Vete, [pcname]. Hablaremos más tarde."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:229
translate spanish reba8mudding_61f77a4c_1:

    # pc "Sure."
    pc "Claro."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:234
translate spanish reba8mudding_a3c096b9:

    # "I try to get my hands up, but I have no experience with fighting and I don't know what I'm doing."
    "Intento levantar las manos, pero no tengo experiencia en peleas y no sé lo que estoy haciendo."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:235
translate spanish reba8mudding_29541e19:

    # "I nearly fall to the ground when Mickey's fist lands cleanly with my jaw, making my head rock back."
    "Casi caigo al suelo cuando el puño de Mickey me impacta de lleno en la mandíbula, haciendo que mi cabeza se eche hacia atrás."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:238
translate spanish reba8mudding_7167e5de:

    # "I manage to stay on my feet and turn expecting another punch to come up at me, but Reba steps between us."
    "Consigo mantenerme en pie y me giro esperando que me llegue otro puñetazo, pero Reba se interpone entre nosotros."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:239
translate spanish reba8mudding_53c501af_2:

    # rb "No! Stop fighting!"
    rb "¡No! ¡Dejad de pelear!"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:240
translate spanish reba8mudding_1cc87b7a:

    # mk "Get out of my way Reba! I'm going to kick his ass!"
    mk "¡Quítate de en medio, Reba! ¡Voy a darle una paliza!"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:241
translate spanish reba8mudding_b0ef0d77:

    # rb "No! Mickey don't, he didn't do anything!"
    rb "¡No! ¡Mickey, no lo hagas, él no ha hecho nada!"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:242
translate spanish reba8mudding_c7a337dd:

    # mk "He's out here trying to fuck you."
    mk "Está aquí fuera intentando tirarse de ti."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:243
translate spanish reba8mudding_cf33bf08:

    # pc "No, I--"
    pc "No, yo..."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:244
translate spanish reba8mudding_f8c3269f:

    # rb "We didn't do nothing, Mickey!"
    rb "¡No hemos hecho nada, Mickey!"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:245
translate spanish reba8mudding_54567e75_2:

    # rb "Just go, [pcname]. I'll talk to you later."
    rb "Vete ya, [pcname]. Hablaremos más tarde."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:246
translate spanish reba8mudding_61f77a4c_2:

    # pc "Sure."
    pc "Claro."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:250
translate spanish reba8mudding_e5760220:

    # "I walk back towards my car, annoyed at the whole situation."
    "Vuelvo hacia mi coche, molesto por toda la situación."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:251
translate spanish reba8mudding_47832cf5:

    # mk "Yeah you better leave city boy. You come out here and mess with my sister again and I'll fucking kill you."
    mk "Sí, mejor que te largues, chico de ciudad. Si vuelves por aquí y vuelves a meterte con mi hermana, te mato, joder."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:252
translate spanish reba8mudding_de895dda:

    # rb "Shut up, Mickey!"
    rb "¡Cállate, Mickey!"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:253
translate spanish reba8mudding_268e6bf6:

    # "I think about going back and finishing this right here, but Reba is already upset, and I'm upset, and I don't think us having a brawl will make the situation any better."
    "Pienso en volver y acabar con esto aquí mismo, pero Reba ya está enfadada, y yo también, y no creo que una pelea entre nosotros vaya a mejorar la situación."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:255
translate spanish reba8mudding_1ae8c9bc:

    # "Plus, I'm not even sure I could take him. He might actually kill me."
    "Además, ni siquiera estoy seguro de poder con él. Podría llegar a matarme."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:258
translate spanish reba8mudding_953ca1e1:

    # "I get into my car and drive away. Hopefully I can spend some more time with Reba later, but this shit with her brother is getting old."
    "Me subo al coche y me voy. Espero poder pasar más tiempo con Reba más tarde, pero esta mierda con su hermano ya me está hartando."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:261
translate spanish reba8mudding_9669528e:

    # "Later..."
    "Más tarde..."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:268
translate spanish reba8b_9c8ee4a8:

    # "I start to get ready for bed and my phone rings. Reba's calling."
    "Empiezo a prepararme para irme a la cama y suena mi teléfono. Es Reba."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:273
translate spanish reba8b_ec87f6ba:

    # pc "Hello."
    pc "Hola."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:274
translate spanish reba8b_611dcce8:

    # rb "Hey, [pcname]."
    rb "Hola, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:276
translate spanish reba8b_2cf6fac4:

    # rb "I just wanted to apologize for Mickey."
    rb "Solo quería disculparme por lo de Mickey."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:277
translate spanish reba8b_3f19332b:

    # rb "He's such a pain in the butt sometimes, you know?"
    rb "A veces es un auténtico pesado, ¿sabes?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:278
translate spanish reba8b_66ecc76b:

    # rb "With Daddy gone, he thinks that it's his job to protect me. But I'm 19. I'm an adult. I can do whatever I want."
    rb "Ahora que papá ya no está, cree que es su deber protegerme. Pero tengo 19 años. Soy adulta. Puedo hacer lo que quiera."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:279
translate spanish reba8b_c1b58d40:

    # rb "Still, I can't convince him to leave it alone."
    rb "Aun así, no consigo convencerlo de que me deje en paz."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:281
translate spanish reba8b_f0842945:

    # rb "So, I'd like to see you again, but it's probably a good idea if you don't come out to the trailer anymore."
    rb "Así que me gustaría volver a verte, pero probablemente sea mejor que no vuelvas a venir a la caravana."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:286
translate spanish reba8b_7bb269b5:

    # rb "Yeah, I guess that's the other option."
    rb "Sí, supongo que esa es la otra opción."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:287
translate spanish reba8b_3090c8da:

    # rb "Okay. I had a good time today, [pcname]. Sorry it didn't go like we planned though."
    rb "Vale. Me lo he pasado bien hoy, [pcname]. Aunque siento que no haya salido como habíamos planeado."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:288
translate spanish reba8b_9e254bb2:

    # rb "Take care. Bye."
    rb "Cuídate. Adiós."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:291
translate spanish reba8b_596474d1:

    # "She hangs up and I put my phone back in my pocket."
    "Ella cuelga y yo vuelvo a guardar el móvil en el bolsillo."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:292
translate spanish reba8b_c8a4994e:

    # "With her family, it just isn't going to work out between us and I don't want to get any more involved."
    "Con su familia, esto entre nosotros no va a funcionar y no quiero involucrarme más."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:294
translate spanish reba8b_cde6c8b5:

    # "I put my phone away and go to sleep."
    "Guardo el móvil y me voy a dormir."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:298
translate spanish reba8b_4e07e53d:

    # rb "Oh I'm so glad you said that. I'd love to."
    rb "Oh, me alegro mucho de que hayas dicho eso. Me encantaría."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:299
translate spanish reba8b_410939a3:

    # rb "I was a little afraid you wouldn't want to see me anymore. I know it's difficult to deal with my family."
    rb "Tenía un poco de miedo de que ya no quisieras verme. Sé que es difícil lidiar con mi familia."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:300
translate spanish reba8b_f09c8cc4:

    # pc "It is. But I like you, Reba. That's what really matters."
    pc "Lo es. Pero me gustas, Reba. Eso es lo que realmente importa."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:301
translate spanish reba8b_5661fd5c:

    # rb "I like you too."
    rb "Tú también me gustas."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:302
translate spanish reba8b_04916afe:

    # pc "So do you want to go on a date sometime?"
    pc "¿Entonces quieres que quedemos algún día?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:304
translate spanish reba8b_c8d6195d:

    # rb "Yes! I really do."
    rb "¡Sí! De verdad que sí."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:305
translate spanish reba8b_af09a7ac:

    # rb "I'll give you a call soon and let you know when I'm available okay?"
    rb "Te llamaré pronto para decirte cuándo estoy libre, ¿vale?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:306
translate spanish reba8b_050f909c:

    # pc "Sounds good."
    pc "Me parece bien."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:307
translate spanish reba8b_91ddb576:

    # rb "Okay. See you later, [pcname]. Good night."
    rb "Vale. Hasta luego, [pcname]. Buenas noches."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:310
translate spanish reba8b_2eac7384:

    # "She hangs up and I put my phone back onto my night stand."
    "Cuelga y vuelvo a dejar el teléfono en la mesita de noche."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:311
translate spanish reba8b_7703588f:

    # "A real date with Reba sounds fun. Something to look forward to."
    "Una cita de verdad con Reba suena divertido. Algo que esperar con ilusión."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba8.rpy:314
translate spanish reba8b_75603258:

    # "I fall asleep, thinking of where I might want to take her."
    "Me quedo dormido, pensando en dónde me gustaría llevarla."

